Through first-person POV experiences, Amaze brings you engaging and entertaining content, centering the storyline around you. Committed to premium VR experiences, all Amaze videos are shot with custom-rigged 3D 4K cameras to deliver the highest quality videos. And you can experience personally curated content based on your interests.

Amaze offers experiences for all, such as:

SURVIVE THE APOCALYPSE - Never fought zombies? No problem - veteran survivors ZombieGoBoom train you from zombie victim to victor.
DANCE THE WALK OF FAME - Stop traffic as you dance with this Venezuelan beauty along Hollywood’s Walk of Fame.
BECOME A BABY SEA LION - Ever wonder what it’s like to be a baby sea lion? Probably not, but get an up close and personal view of these animals as one of their own!
JOIN AN INTIMATE CONCERT - Queensland’s “Best Urban Song of the Year” Winner (2017), Romy, brings you into her world through “Smile”.

Download the app today, and be amazed with a new point of view.
